    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >添加至愿望清单，不要错过发售折扣！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/25a58481da79dd86c8ff674ba875f797.poster.avif?t=1691098733\" width=616 height=38 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/25a58481da79dd86c8ff674ba875f797.webm?t=1691098733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/25a58481da79dd86c8ff674ba875f797.mp4?t=1691098733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与动态画作互动</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/532bad1874704578d5bf7b4186db4759.poster.avif?t=1691098733\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/532bad1874704578d5bf7b4186db4759.webm?t=1691098733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/532bad1874704578d5bf7b4186db4759.mp4?t=1691098733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>当你触摸这些画作时，它们会栩栩如生。<br>遇见奇怪的角色，寻找线索，揭开谜团。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >绘制符号解谜题</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/403dc32a466fba048e054db94dfaa53b.poster.avif?t=1691098733\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/403dc32a466fba048e054db94dfaa53b.webm?t=1691098733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/403dc32a466fba048e054db94dfaa53b.mp4?t=1691098733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这些符号会改变画作，有时也会影响现实世界。<br>尝试不同的符号，看看它们的效果！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索超现实世界</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/9a2f1446972623487ea3e7538080b2a2.poster.avif?t=1691098733\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/9a2f1446972623487ea3e7538080b2a2.webm?t=1691098733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/9a2f1446972623487ea3e7538080b2a2.mp4?t=1691098733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探索一个超现实的世界，逻辑规则并不总是适用。<br>发现受到画家艺术影响的地方，并为其增添你自己的风格。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >透过画家的故事发现艺术的价值</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/ba2cd537e655f0dd5a0ee71f611cef07.poster.avif?t=1691098733\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/ba2cd537e655f0dd5a0ee71f611cef07.webm?t=1691098733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339590/extras/ba2cd537e655f0dd5a0ee71f611cef07.mp4?t=1691098733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在探索逝去画家的故事中揭示艺术的深刻价值。<br>在旅程中，你将对艺术表达的力量以及它对我们周围世界的影响有所领悟。",
